{"tid":1162441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"議員說話要人教！日正妹主播怒脫稿演出　網讚翻：中肯","createTime":"2019-05-20T01:08:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T03:49:32.000Z","uid":32511,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7fae4203b7183560b0d955ec1ae29fa051cab756","tid":1162441,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:08:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hh70ZsdrTGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fhh70ZsdrTGU&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ14dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=a7670b21\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hh70ZsdrTGU</a><br />\n<br />\n31歲日本甜美主播三田友梨佳，日前在播報日本執政黨自民黨「派發的防止失言手冊」新聞時竟脫稿演出，質疑「國會議員的資質到底怎麼了？」引發網友在推特瘋傳這段20秒影片，直呼「說得太中肯了」。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LBw8acg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLBw8acg.png&h=dd204755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合日媒報導，日本執政黨自民黨近日因該黨議員接連失言下台，讓他為了避免再次類似事件發生，對黨員特別製作「防止失言手冊」給議員。沒想到日本富士電視台（FNN）甜美主播三田友梨佳在現場直播時看到該新聞字幕內容，卻忍不住脫稿演出，說出自己的心聲，直言：「我們需要的不是手冊，難道不是判斷力嗎？」並認為，不因是他人告訴你說什麼和什麼不該說，而是對自己說的話負責，且質疑「國會議員的資質到底怎麼了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/px9E1i7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpx9E1i7.png&h=f4dd9dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此言論立即引發網友拍下畫面在推特上瘋傳，許多網友看到影片後，紛紛大讚三田友梨佳表示「該言論超中肯」、「說得太棒」、「批評得超好」、「本世紀最佳評論」、「太狂了！看來會有許久看不到主播了」。"},{"pid":"b7afcdd25515496799e4106c0543ffdbf9a9ecd5","tid":1162441,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:34:11.000Z","msg":"幾好屌，個款"},{"pid":"aa8de27ebc820062054c0431f472e653dab46113","tid":1162441,"uid":117251,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:45:34.000Z","msg":"標題:<br />\n日正妹主播怒脫....................稿演出"},{"pid":"dc9c6b0d8b1f8e729213afa21e5bf3056d0a41b1","tid":1162441,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:50:29.000Z","msg":"日本咁多AV，係一個好咸濕嘅地方<br />\n但人哋報新聞時都知道要著得端莊<br />\n反觀cctvb成日扮道德判官<br />\n但班女主播就成日deep V 成身lace出鏡報新聞報天氣<br />\n引小朋友同老人家打j<br />\n袁志偉真係好賤"},{"pid":"cd14ffa75f30f49e2724996560146517fc7f54f5","tid":1162441,"uid":49197,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://desk-drawer.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mitayurika-667x720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdesk-drawer.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F09%2Fmitayurika-667x720.jpg&h=409b4fe5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d6f76146ca9592a04d14dfb34f27a13bf7ab323","tid":1162441,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:53:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a27f4c7e740c09925b109705f35b767489d123b7","tid":1162441,"uid":57329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"人又靚又有思想又感言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720e9227a6f5f51f1b2917071e861164fde6394e","tid":1162441,"uid":41411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:54:59.000Z","msg":"日本執政黨自民黨近日因該黨議員接連失言下台<br />\n<br />\n香港唔會出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573878652dad9f68d3b05fe7869e728f01913b9d","tid":1162441,"uid":227581,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:56:09.000Z","msg":"被電視台打壓<br />\n無工開 無糧出 失業<br />\n然後行內打壓<br />\n絕路之下洗哂啲錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後下海拍AV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46b6570a153881fcb91a36b6b14bdba7ad6b67b","tid":1162441,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"cd14ffa75f30f49e2724996560146517fc7f54f5","tid":1162441,"uid":49197,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://desk-draw